# The Key Depot
### Secure your passwords

This is an application which can be used to store all your passwords for various email Ids. For a developer like us, would own lots of email ids for various purposes. Remembering the email ids and its passwords is a hectic job(For myself :D). We tend to forget the passwords.

This is application would remember those passwords for you. Though you may have to remember one password to access this application(No way out :D).

**The Key Depot** is in its infancy and will grow bigger in future(obviously! :D);

Cheers;
